erson (footballer)|Wayne Henderson]] (to [[Preston North End]])}}\n{{Fs player|no=1|nat=ENG|pos=GK|name=[[Scott Flinders]] (on loan from [[Crystal Palace F.C.|Crystal Palace]])}}\n{{Fs player|no=12|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=[[Richard Carpenter (footballer)|Richard Carpenter]] (contract terminated in February 2007)<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_conf/6400129.stm|title=Carpenter explains Welling switch|publisher=BBC Sport}}</ref>}}\n{{Fs player|no=21|nat=SWI|pos=FW|name=[[Maheta Molango]] (contract terminated in February 2007)<ref>{{cite news|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721112923/http://www.seagulls.co.uk/page/Latest/0,,10433~974616,00.html|title=Maheta moves on|publisher=Brighton & Hove Albion F.C.}}</ref>}}\n{{Fs player|no=22|nat=TUR|pos=FW|name=[[Colin Kazim-Richards]] (to [[Sheffield United]])}}\n{{Fs player|no=22|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=[[Sam Williams (footballer)|Sam Williams]] (on loan from [[Aston Villa]])}}\n{{fs mid}}\n{{Fs player|no=22|nat=ENG|pos=FW|name=[[Dean Bowditch]] (on loan from [[Ipswich Town]])}}\n{{Fs player|no=33|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=[[Keith Lowe]] (on loan from [[Wolverhampton Wanderers|Wolves]])}}\n{{Fs player|no=33|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=[[Andrew Whing]] (on loan from [[Coventry City]])}}\n{{Fs player|no=34|nat=ENG|pos=FW|name=[[Tony Stokes]] (on loan from [[West Ham United]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=34|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=[[Alistair John]] (on loan from [[Charlton Athletic]])}}\n{{fs end}}\n\n==Results==\n===League One===\n{{Football box collapsible\n|date=5 August 2006\n|time=15:00\n|score=0-1\n|report=https://www.11v11.com/matches/rotherham-united-v-brighton-and-hove-albion-05-august-2006-274179/\n|team1=[[Rotherham United]]\n|goals1=\n|team2=[[Brighton & Hove Albion]]\n|goals2=[[Alex Revell|Revell]] {{goal|43}}<br>[[Dean Cox|Cox]] {{sent off|0|45}}\n|stadium=[[Millmoor]]\n|location=[[Rotherham]]\n|attendance=4,998\n|referee=Colin Webster\n|result=W\n}}\n\n{{Football box collapsible\n|date=8 August 2006\n|time=19:45\n